# Trellis runs its labs in Linux containers and a POSIX shell. Force LF on
# checkout everywhere so shell rc files and scripts (e.g. trellis-bashrc.sh)
# are never corrupted to CRLF when cloned on Windows, which would break the
# in-container terminal and the .mjs runners.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Belt-and-suspenders for the executable/interpreted scripts.
*.sh   text eol=lf
*.mjs  text eol=lf
